OL,3,C'Slapping therapist' found guilty of
OL,4,Cmanslaughter
OL,6,FAn alternative healer who failed to
OL,7,Fget medical help for a 71-year-old
OL,8,Fdiabetic woman who died after she
OL,9,Fstopped taking insulin at his slapping
OL,10,Ftherapy workshop has been found guilty
OL,11,Fof her manslaughter.
OL,13,FDanielle Carr-Gomm died at Cleeve
OL,14,FHouse in Seend, Wiltshire, in October
OL,15,F2016 while taking part in the Paida
OL,16,FLajin therapy event, which sees
OL,17,Fpatients being slapped or slapping
OL,18,Fthemselves repeatedly.
