OL,3,C'Slapping therapist' found guilty of
OL,4,Cmanslaughter
OL,6,FHongchi Xiao, of Cloudbreak,
OL,7,FCalifornia, was convicted by the jury
OL,8,Fat Winchester Crown Court of the
OL,9,Fmanslaughter by gross negligence of
OL,10,FMrs Carr-Gomm, from Lewes, East Sussex.
OL,12,FThe 61-year-old was extradited for the
OL,13,Ftrial from Australia, where he had
OL,14,Fpreviously been prosecuted over the
OL,15,Fdeath of a six-year-old boy who also
OL,16,Fdied after his parents withdrew his
OL,17,Finsulin medication after attending the
OL,18,Fdefendant's workshop in Sydney.
