OL,3,C'Slapping therapist' found guilty of
OL,4,Cmanslaughter
OL,6,FThe court heard that Mrs Carr-Gomm,
OL,7,Fwho was diagnosed with Type 1 diabetes
OL,8,Fin 1999, was left "howling in pain" as
OL,9,Fshe became seriously ill before she
OL,10,Fdied on the fourth day of the workshop.
OL,12,FDuncan Atkinson KC, prosecuting, told
OL,13,Fthe jury that Mrs Carr-Gomm had sought
OL,14,Falternatives to her insulin medication
OL,15,Ffor type 1 diabetes because of her
OL,16,Fvegetarianism and fear of needles.
OL,18,FShe had first joined a Paida Lajin
OL,19,Fworkshop, which means "slap and
OL,20,Fstretch", run by the defendant in
OL,21,FBulgaria in July 2016.
