OL,6,FShe became seriously ill after
OL,7,Fstopping her insulin medicine before
OL,8,Fshe restarted and subsequently
OL,9,Frecovered.
OL,11,FMr Atkinson described how Mrs Carr-
OL,12,FGomm went on to attend another of
OL,13,FXiao's workshops in Wiltshire in
OL,14,FOctober of that year.
OL,16,FThe court had heard how Xiao said
OL,17,F"well done" to Mrs Carr-Gomm, after
OL,18,Fshe told the group she had stopped
OL,19,Ftaking her insulin at the week-long
OL,20,Fretreat, and she became seriously ill.
