OL,6,FMr Atkinson said that by the third day
OL,7,F"she was vomiting, tired and weak, and
OL,8,Fby the evening she was howling in pain
OL,9,Fand unable to respond to questions".
OL,11,FA chef at the workshop, Teresa Hayes,
OL,12,Ftold jurors Mrs Carr-Gomm was
OL,13,F"delirious" and "frothing at the
OL,14,Fmouth" before she died, adding that
OL,15,Fshe wanted to call an ambulance but
OL,16,Ftrusted those with more experience of
OL,17,Fthe holistic healing method.
