OL,6,FMr Atkinson described how the
OL,7,Fdefendant failed to get medical help
OL,8,Ffor Mrs Carr-Gomm before she died in
OL,9,Fthe early hours of the fourth day.
OL,11,FThe prosecutor said: "Those who had
OL,12,Freceived and accepted the defendant's
OL,13,Fteachings misinterpreted Mrs Carr-
OL,14,FGomm's condition as a healing crisis."
OL,16,FHe said that Xiao had been an
OL,17,F"exponent" of Paida Lajin for 10 years
OL,18,Fand had written a book on it.
