OL,6,F"In a book that he wrote about Paida
OL,7,FLajin, the defendant asserted that the
OL,8,Ftaking of insulin leads to liver and
OL,9,Feye problems, and that in contrast the
OL,10,FPaida Lajin was 'safer and more
OL,11,Freliable than existing healing
OL,12,Fpractices' which would result in
OL,13,F'significant improvement' or full
OL,14,Frecovery in 90% of cases, including
OL,15,Fcases of diabetes."
