OL,10,Ftreating and dealing with her
OL,11,Fdiabetes, and was very interested in
OL,12,Falternative and holistic medicine and
OL,13,Ftherapies.
OL,15,F"I know she was desperate to try and
OL,16,Fcure herself of this disease.
OL,18,F"She always maintained a healthy
